<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Hannah Skibbe</title>
  <style>
    /* --- CSS Variables for Easy Theming --- */
    :root {
      --bg-color: #fdfdfd;
      --text-color: #222222;
      --nav-link-color: #555555;
      --accent-color: #000000;
      /* Using a clean sans-serif for UI, and serif for headings */
      --font-main: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      --font-heading: "Georgia", "Times New Roman", serif;
    }

    /* --- Reset & Base Styles --- */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      background-color: var(--bg-color);
      color: var(--text-color);
      font-family: var(--font-main);
      line-height: 1.6;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 3rem 5%;
    }

    /* --- Header & Navigation --- */
    header {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    h1.site-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: normal;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    nav {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    nav ul li a {
      color: var(--nav-link-color);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover {
      color: var(--accent-color);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 4px;
    }

    /* --- Main Content Area --- */
    main {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
    }

    h2.section-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    /* CSS Grid to split the image and the text */
    .about-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2.5fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    /* Image Styling */
    .portrait-wrapper figure {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .portrait-wrapper img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      background-color: #eaeaea; /* Placeholder block */
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .portrait-wrapper figcaption {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #777777;
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* Typography inside the bio */
    .bio-content p {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #333333;
    }

    /* --- Responsive Breakpoints --- */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .portrait-wrapper {
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      nav ul {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      h1.site-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Site Header -->
  <header>
    <h1 class="site-title">Hannah Skibbe</h1>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#words">Words</a></li>
        <li><a href="#resume">Resume</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main>
    <h2 class="section-title">About Hannah</h2>
    
    <div class="about-container">
      <!-- Left Column: Portrait -->
      <div class="portrait-wrapper">
        <figure>
          <!-- Replace the src below with your actual image URL -->
          <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5671993769a91a96f52bb4f2/1460615926621-0Q1ORQ3AX34SAZ257HDD/image-asset.jpeg?format=2500w" alt="A portrait of the artist circa 1997">
          <figcaption>A portrait of the artist circa 1997</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Column: Bio Text -->
      <div class="bio-content">
        <p>Hannah is a writer and archivist from Minneapolis, now based in Brooklyn, New York. She graduated from the University of Minnesota in 2016 with a BA in Studies in Media and Cinema Culture. In 2023, she earned her MLIS from Queens College, where her research focused on film and television archives in the streaming era.</p>
        
        <p>She is currently on the steering committee of XFR Collective, a 501c3 organization dedicated to providing education, equipment, and low cost digitization and preservation access to video artists and community members. With XFR, she has worked with many artist's collections, including Kiki Smith, Joan Jubela, Alan Moore, and many others.</p>
        
        <p>She spends most of her free time thinking about television, which she believes is the perfect medium.</p>
        
        <p>You can find her in various places online and in real life.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
